                  </persName>
            , faith, that on Tuesday evening, between eleven and twelve, standing at the Ship and Star door, an ale-house in East Smithfield, and many more present, words arose, and this informant and 
               <persName id="t17830723-1-person69">
                  Antonio
                   Da Costa
               <interp inst="t17830723-1-person69" type="surname" value="Da Costa"></interp>
