                     <interp inst="t17830723-1-person72" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             a knife and stabbed him in four different parts of his body, and this informant further faith, that he is sure that Pinto is the person that stabbed him, and Da Costa was standing, aiding, and assisting at the transaction."</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17830723-1-person73">
                  WILLIAM
                   ADAIR
               <interp inst="t17830723-1-person73" type="surname" value="ADAIR"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830723-1-person73" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830723-1-person73" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
